  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male or female, 18 years and older

          -  Written informed consent

          -  Diabetes mellitus type 1 or 2

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with mental diseases

          -  Pregnancy or lactation

          -  Ascites

          -  Continued alcohol consumption (&gt; 21 drinks/week for male and &gt; 14 drinks/week for
             female patients)

          -  Chronic liver disease (viral hepatitis, autoimmune hepatitis, PBC, PSC,
             hemochromatosis, M Wilson)

          -  Hepatocellular carcinoma/ Liver metastasis
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
